data.description: **Sellers will consider reasonable offers** Welcome to this delightful EXPANDED patio home in Sun City! With two bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms, and a generous 1,591 square feet of space, it's the perfect home. The enclosed lanai adds extra room for your enjoyment. The home features a new roof from 2020 and updated carpets and floors from 2018. Plus, the HOA covers water, sewer, landscaping, trash removal, roof repairs and replacements, pest control, and exterior maintenance, making life hassle-free. You'll love the convenient location, close to shopping, golf, and sports stadiums. This pet-friendly community doesn't allow rentals, ensuring a friendly and stable atmosphere. Join us in Sun City, where there's never a dull moment!
